definitions.definition: ( music ) A syllable used in solfège to represent the fifth note of a major scale .

main_definition: ( music ) A syllable used in solfège to represent the fifth note of a major scale .

definitions.definition: A type of dairy product, made especially in Japan between the seventh and tenth centuries, by reducing milk by boiling it.
